description:
Get exclusive access to exciting content and our entire DVD library all while helping to support us at https://patreon.com/fountainview

===

Join Fountainview Academy students and staff in the workplace. This series of short videos will explore the many different vocational training areas that give Fountainview Academy students real life experience, a chance to put theory into practice, and most importantly, an opportunity to build character.

Music: Morning Walk by Johny Easton
